extract_html:
MEMBERSHIP RULES
  • Members must bring their Membership Card to the Club every day. ...
  • Members must check in and out upon entering and exiting the Club by presenting their membership card.
  • Members must remain within designated areas.
  • Members are responsible for any valuables/money brought to the Club.
More items...
